    "body": "Tried a new install with `paru` using the `starship-git` package to see if compiling it on my machine would fix the issue. The installation failed with:\n\n```\ntest result: FAILED. 936 passed; 203 failed; 39 ignored; 0 measured; 0 filtered out; finished in 1.30s\n```\n\nSome of these tests are:\n\n```\nthread 'modules::zig::tests::folder_with_zig_file' panicked at src/modules/zig.rs:82:9:\nassertion `left == right` failed\n  left: Some(\"via \\u{1b}[1;33m↯ v0.6.0 \\u{1b}[0m\")\n right: Some(\"via \\u{1b}[1;38;2;229;200;144m↯ v0.6.0 \\u{1b}[0m\")\n```\n\n```\nthread 'modules::dotnet::tests::shows_multiple_tfms' panicked at src/modules/dotnet.rs:644:9:\nassertion `left == right` failed\n  left: Some(\"via \\u{1b}[1;38;2;140;170;238m.NET v3.1.103 🎯 netstandard2.0;net461 \\u{1b}[0m\")\n right: Some(\"via \\u{1b}[1;34m.NET v3.1.103 🎯 netstandard2.0;net461 \\u{1b}[0m\")\n```\n\n```\nthread 'modules::dotnet::tests::shows_pinned_in_directory_with_global_json' panicked at src/modules/dotnet.rs:644:9:\nassertion `left == right` failed\n  left: Some(\"via \\u{1b}[1;38;2;140;170;238m.NET v1.2.3 \\u{1b}[0m\")\n right: Some(\"via \\u{1b}[1;34m.NET v1.2.3 \\u{1b}[0m\")\n```\n\nMaybe the difference in ANSI 'characters'  is the problem?",
