    "body": "Ok after doing a lot more tinkering now I know \"sort of\" where the problem is. It's the starship config file. When I removed that and used the default config the bug is gone. Anyone know whats wrong with this config that could cause the bug?:\n\n[starship.toml](https://github.com/hydr0nium/configs/blob/main/starship/.config/starship.toml)\n\nEdit:\n\nThe **official catppuccin template** on this page:\nhttps://starship.rs/presets/catppuccin-powerline\nis also broken for me\n\nEdit 2:\n\nTested [gruvbox-rainbow](https://starship.rs/presets/gruvbox-rainbow) to check if all configs are broken. But no, its just the one above",
